OL,3,CMan, 76, appears in court after
OL,4,Cchildren fell ill at summer camp
OL,6,FA 76-year-old man has been remanded in
OL,7,Fcustody charged with child cruelty
OL,8,Foffences after children became unwell
OL,9,Fat a summer camp in Leicestershire.
OL,11,FJon Ruben, of Wayte Court in
OL,12,FRuddington, Nottinghamshire, appeared
OL,13,Fat Leicester Magistrates' Court on
OL,14,FSaturday morning charged with three
OL,15,Fcounts of wilfully assaulting, ill-
OL,16,Ftreating, neglecting, abandoning or
OL,17,Fexposing children in a manner likely
OL,18,Fto cause them unnecessary suffering or
OL,19,Finjury to health, relating to three
OL,20,Fboys at the summer camp between July
OL,21,F25 and July 29.
